  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LURK</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Mercer, a sellsword scout, and sole survivor of a mercenary company butchered by an unrelenting demonic force from beyond. <strong>Lurk is a gripping first-person survival horror set in a dark medieval fantasy world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/fe47008fcc630c006b5b4c25477ba079.poster.avif?t=1772246144\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/fe47008fcc630c006b5b4c25477ba079.webm?t=1772246144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/fe47008fcc630c006b5b4c25477ba079.mp4?t=1772246144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival horror in a terrifying open world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate using only headings with a fully in-world compass system - no traditional map</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the vast expanse that is the Farlands; a once flourishing continent now defiled by a demonic invasion.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Run, hide, and fend off a myriad of horrifying monsters that will roam the land freely, and pursue you at any moment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scavenge the world for supplies and ration them effectively to survive the ever-growing demonic threat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover lost lore through ancient texts, scattered notes, and latent memories.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the mystery behind who, or what, is responsible for the death of your mercenary band, and put an end to the demonic invasion that plagues the land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/bb015f29f2716fc53a9ce59cd181dbfb.poster.avif?t=1772246144\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/bb015f29f2716fc53a9ce59cd181dbfb.webm?t=1772246144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/bb015f29f2716fc53a9ce59cd181dbfb.mp4?t=1772246144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A dark forest shrouded in the blanket of night, a labyrinth of rocky crags housing unseen horrors, and a dimension of pure torment are just some of the terrifying environments you will find yourself in as you explore the expanse of the Farlands. Demons, monstrosities, and terrors of all kinds roam the land, forcing you to ration supplies and survive at all costs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/a04413f67e51d4feb4cbcd22a4e36ee7.poster.avif?t=1772246144\" width=1170 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/a04413f67e51d4feb4cbcd22a4e36ee7.webm?t=1772246144\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/527260/extras/a04413f67e51d4feb4cbcd22a4e36ee7.mp4?t=1772246144\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience true fantasy horror now in the world of <strong>Lurk</strong>.</p>",
